This project is a native Android wrapper for three upstream open source
projects:
  - Hermes Agent by Nous Research (MIT) — https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent
  - Hermes WebUI by Nicolas Esquerre (MIT) — https://github.com/nesquena/hermes-webui
  - HuggingMes by somratpro (MIT) — https://github.com/somratpro/HuggingMes

All chat and agent functionality is provided by those upstream projects;
this app only contributes the Android shell (Compose UI, encrypted
credential storage, native sessions drawer, WebView configuration). The
shell is released under the MIT License below. None of the upstream code
is included in this repo.

